{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Community-maintained collection of language packs for REAPER\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Contributors\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Installation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Copy and paste this URL in Extensions > ReaPack > Import a repository:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \f1 https://github.com/ReaTeam/LangPacks/raw/master/index.xml\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Contributing\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Upload your LangPack here to offer download from REAPER and auto-update for your language file!\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/ReaTeam/LangPacks/fork"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Fork
}}}
 this repository in your GitHub account\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Upload your .ReaperLangPack file in the {\f1 Translations} directory\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Insert metadata at the top (check out the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/cfillion/reapack-index/wiki/Examples#language-pack"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
package examples
}}}
 and reapack-index's {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/cfillion/reapack-index/wiki/Packaging-Documentation"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
packaging documentation
}}}
).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab Send a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request-from-a-fork/"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
pull request
}}}
 here, done!\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Non-ReaPack LangPacks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Other REAPER langpacks are only avaible on {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://stash.reaper.fm/tag/Language-Packs"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
stash
}}}
. Please contact their authors and invite them to contribute here!\par}
